<a href="https://iono.fm/e/643117">Content hosted by iono.fm</a> Top 5 finalist in the Chivas Venture SA leg of the competition, Glenda Tutt, explains the inspiration behind her project Mpower menstrual cups in conversation with Moneyweb. The Chivas Venture competition gives away $1 million in no-strings funding, and expert coaching at the Chivas Venture Accelerator Programme, to social entrepreneurs who blend profit with purpose. The winner of the SA leg will be announced on January 23. Brought to you by Chivas Venture.